      "content": "hey, i was out for a run in stanley park and i tripped really hard on some tree roots. my ankle is super swollen now and it hurts a lot. i cant really walk on it or put any weight on it without it feeling like it's gonna snap. i dont really want to go to the clinic if i dont have to, can i just do the RICE thing (rest, ice, compression, elevation) for a few days and see if it gets better?",
