      "content": "It is very difficult to tell if it's a simple sprain or something more serious just by watching it for 48 hours. Severe swelling and inability to bear weight are red flags that warrant immediate medical assessment. Ibuprofen can help manage pain, but it does not diagnose an injury, and waiting could allow a minor issue to become much worse. Please prioritize getting an X-ray to rule out a break.",
